BufferedReader	java.io.BufferedReader	java.io	String	Medium
Console	java.io.Console	java.io	Text/Password	Rare
System.out.print()	â€”	â€”	Output to console	âœ… Yes
ğŸ§  5. Key Points

Always close your input streams using .close().

Handle exceptions using try-catch when using BufferedReader.

System.out is an instance of PrintStream.

Prefer Scanner for beginner-friendly user input.
